About Gangarampura

According to Census 2011 information the location code or village code of Gangarampura village is 110464. Gangarampura village is located in Kairana tehsil of Muzaffarnagar district in Uttar Pradesh, India. It is situated 28km away from sub-district headquarter Kairana (tehsildar office) and 62km away from district headquarter Muzaffarnagar. As per 2009 stats, Gangarampura village is also a gram panchayat.

The total geographical area of village is 177.11 hectares. Gangarampura has a total population of 2,934 peoples, out of which male population is 1,570 while female population is 1,364. Literacy rate of gangarampura village is 58.86% out of which 67.13% males and 49.34% females are literate. There are about 503 houses in gangarampura village. Pincode of gangarampura village locality is 247778.

Kairana is nearest town to gangarampura village for all major economic activities.
